EN: The kidnapped hostages are currently receiving rescue assistance.

ZH: 警方成功解救了全部人质。
EN: The police successfully rescued all the hostages.

ZH: 人质被困在这座建筑内。
EN: The hostages are trapped inside this building.

ZH: 人质们受到了严重的心理创伤。
EN: The hostages have suffered severe psychological trauma.

ZH: 绑架者一直在威胁要杀害人质。
EN: The kidnapper has been threatening to kill the hostages.

