EN: The safety of the hostages' lives is of utmost importance during the negotiation process.

ZH: 救援队伍正在制定解救人质的计划。
EN: The rescue team is devising a plan to free the hostages.

ZH: 人质们被拘禁在一个地下室里。
EN: The hostages are held captive in an underground cellar.

ZH: 武装分子将人质用作要挟的工具。
EN: The armed militants use the hostages as a tool for blackmail.

ZH: 人质们被囚禁已经持续了数周。
EN: The hostages have been held captive for weeks.

ZH: 安全人员正密切监视着被劫持的人质。
EN: Security personnel are closely monitoring the kidnapped hostages.

ZH: 人质被扣留在这座建筑物的顶层。
EN: The hostages are being held captive on the top floor of this building.

ZH: 谈判代表与劫持者就人质的释放进行了艰难的交涉。
EN: Negotiators engaged in difficult negotiations with the hostage-takers for their release.

ZH: 联合国已派遣特使前往现场解救人质。
EN: The United Nations has dispatched a special envoy to rescue the hostages on-site.

ZH: 已经获救的人质正在接受身体检查。
EN: The rescued hostages are undergoing medical examinations.

